== GNOME Sudoku ==

[[File:GnomeSudoku_screenshot1.png|thumb|right|150px|GNOME Sudoku]]

This is an application for playing the popular sudoku logic puzzle game, in which one must fill a 9 by 9 square with the correct digits. GNOME Sudoku is meant to have as simple, unobstrusive an interface as possible while still providing features that make playing difficult Sudoku more fun.

