== Me and My Shadow ==

[[File:meandmyshadow_screenshot1.png|thumb|right|150px|Me and My Shadow [http://meandmyshadow.sourceforge.net/?media.html media]]]

Me and My Shadow is a free libre puzzle/platform game in which you try to reach the exit by solving puzzles. Spikes, moving blocks, fragile blocks and much more stand between you and the exit. Record your moves and let your shadow mimic them to reach blocks you couldn't reach alone. It features over 40 levels and 18 different block types and also comes with an ingame map editor. View a YouTube demo [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UUcdtxoO5Lw here].

