== Pingus ==

[[File:Pingus_screenshot1.png|thumb|right|150px]]

Pingus is a free clone of the popular Lemmings game. Your goal is to guide a horde of penguins through a world full of obstacles and penguin traps to safety. Although penguins (unlike lemmings) are rather smart, they sometimes lack the necessary overview and now rely on you to save them. You can view a YouTube demo [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bs8Xq9d4o7Q here].

